data.description: Well maintained, beautifully updated 3 BR, 2 Bath bi-level, in the desirable Beechwood Trails community.  Wonderful curb appeal with stone accented exterior & mature landscaping.  Flexible living space you can use to fit your lifestyle.  Split entry Foyer, steps up to the main level with Living/Dining Rm, Eat-in Kitchen with sliding glass door to Deck, 2 generous Bedrooms & updated Full Bath with tub/shower, new vanity & lighted medicine cabinet.  Expansive Lower Level Family Room with fireplace, 3rd Bedroom, 2nd Full Bath & Utility/Laundry Room.  2 Car Garage, fenced & open yard areas, Deck & Patio, plus 12x16 storage space with overhead door.  Community Park with pool, playground, basketball.  Freshly Painted Interior, Newer Roof, New: Flooring, Range, HVAC, Water Heater, and more
